
- improve output readability
- directive to link to a test in the docs but include it in the suite
- option to specify that a context should have its own process
- implement acceptance testing DSL along the lines of

  Testing hello.rb
    I am nobody
      When I read from /
      it returns Hello, world!
    I am user1
      My password is asdfasdf
      When I read from /
      it returns Hello, world!
    Bob is user2
      his password is asdfasdf
      When he reads from /
      it returns Hello, world!

